      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that satisfies the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a drop of rain, let alone winter salt. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries the distinct scent of a new vehicle. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance milestone performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for someone who demands perfection.",
